_sText:
This is a final version of de_beersheba_conflict. There have been several changes from the first changes including but not limited to:
  • a 3D skybox
  • addition of soundscapes
  • addition of a sewer
  • drastic rework of environment to make it feel more real
  • addition of more props
  • changes to T spawn area
  • changes to bombsite A
  • added another entry to center building
There are a total of 50 spawn points, but I would not suggest utilization of all spawn points due to the size of the map.

Please rate and leave feedback.
